/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都有諗過走<br />\n但呢啲因素令到變相捉住左我無得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"我而家咁諗 如果真係想走 冇野捉得住你 <br />\n捉到 證明你都唔係好想走姐"},{"pid":"f0d093e2feca2e4cba465bf2a1aed1da556a39c9","tid":1153702,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:09:57.000Z","msg":"讀完個科 順勢做埋個行 <br />\n無話想唔想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02d7ed2c2fe8283e23ff62d3679c59f0eecafe7","tid":1153702,"uid":73333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:16:24.000Z","msg":"錢"},{"pid":"165b540bbe02be0fa9a4e33901d35a529019d778","tid":1153702,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"999c623fcff2d3673c9af0a974995519aa7d6126","tid":1153702,"uid":139838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92cb0e60551276becec3579ab414d0b425c8614c","tid":1153702,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb707c741904d9d300a58259a417336d47b055f8","tid":1153702,"uid":139838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:05:07.000Z","msg":"對你黎講 你嘅目標係咪淨係揾錢<br />\n如果係 你可以為左呢個目標犧牲啲咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:19:27.000Z","msg":"做雞唔搵錢 唔通閪癢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪同普通打工一樣 犧牲時間, 勞力囉 <br />\n仲可以犧牲乜嘢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:00:42.000Z","msg":"仲有 人地對你嘅尊重 自己尊嚴 道德 貞潔 未來另一半會介意/定你已經放棄左揾 <br />\n為左錢 真係值得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T03:35:13.000Z","msg":"衰嘅你出去做7仔 做M記 <br />\n好少少嘅你去做警犬 做食環 <br />\n你有尊嚴咩? <br />\n打份工嘅好多都無尊嚴咖啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n道德 貞潔 仲on9 <br />\n道德 貞潔可以當飯食? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8ccfef96833c800b9246d338